import React from 'react'

const RemoveFromCartIcon = () => {
    return (
        <svg
            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
            width="24"
            height="24"
            fill="none"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
        >
            <path
                fill="#293644"
                fillRule="evenodd"
                d="M11 2a1 1 0 00-1 1v1h4V3a1 1 0 00-1-1h-2zm5 2V3a3 3 0 00-3-3h-2a3 3 0 00-3 3v1H3a1 1 0 000 2h.105l1.703 15.331A3 3 0 007.79 24h8.42a3 3 0 002.982-2.669L20.895 6H21a1 1 0 100-2h-5zm2.883 2H5.117l1.68 15.11a1 1 0 00.993.89h8.42a1 1 0 00.994-.89L18.883 6zM10 9a1 1 0 011 1v8a1 1 0 11-2 0v-8a1 1 0 011-1zm4 0a1 1 0 011 1v8a1 1 0 11-2 0v-8a1 1 0 011-1z"
                clipRule="evenodd"
            ></path>
        </svg>
    )
}

export default RemoveFromCartIcon
